lead_paragraph: QUARTERLY REPORTS Earnings season begins in earnest with the second-quarter report of Alcoa on Monday. Other earnings: Chevron and Pepsi Bottling, on Tuesday; Genentech and Yum Brands on Wednesday; Marriott, on Thursday; and General Electric, on Friday.
